node.text: The best trip so far 🥰🥰🥰 It feels good to be able to spoil myself.. I work hard so yes I’m gonna play harder.. I love to show a person how to treat me.. If I can do this for myself then what you think you gone do 🙌🏽🤩 I’m turning up all week! I deserve this and every other blessings that’s coming my way .. I have done the work and will continue to do the work.. what ever I can hope dream or imagine I will manifest it in the natural realm 🙏🏽 It is already mines 💎🥰 Ase’ Ase’ Ase’ 🥰🤗

node.text: This is a very powerful message that I receive. I’m letting Nashville Tennessee know that I will be coming to “host” only and not perform at the venue because I will no longer put music out that is not going to help “US” as a unit! I will no longer put out music that will bash “US” as a whole. God is working on me in a mighty way and I’m glad things didn’t go the way I really wanted it to concerning my music because one thing we all do know is I’m very great at it but I refuse to put out music that is going to bash our black men and they should consider doing the same to “US WOMEN” we need to stop being the enemy amongst ourselves! It’s time to “wake up” and speak on what really matters and that’s the injustice that we receive on a daily basis. I can go on and on but I’d rather write it in music. If you don’t see me at the event this evening it will be because  the promoter didn’t accept me not wanting to perform a song that I wrote out of anger for retaliation for all these rappers that keep downing us as women in their songs (and themselves) It’s time for us to work together and not against each other! There is POWER in numbers! Thank you GOD for this revelation/truth! I will not serve on the ENEMIES side no longer Amen 🙏🏽🧜🏽‍♀️as soon as I uploaded this I called the promoter and told what I just shared with you all so YES I will be in Nashville Tennessee this afternoon but I won’t be performing. I will perform again as soon as I get back in the studio to make music that’s gonna help unify US 🙏🏽

I have done the work and will continue to do the work.. what ever I can hope dream or imagine I will manifest it in the natural realm 🙏🏽 It is already mines 💎🥰 Ase’ Ase’ Ase’ 🥰🤗
